  * Day 4: Claude Code baked into the ISO.
  * /usr/bin/vibeos-claude-setup — interactive wizard (kdialog UI).
  * Anthropic API key stored in KDE Wallet via secret-tool (libsecret).
  * /etc/profile.d/vibeos-claude.sh exports ANTHROPIC_API_KEY from keyring.
  * ~/workspace scaffolded with permissive .claude/settings.json.
  * "Start Coding with Claude" desktop launcher → Konsole + claude.
  * Claude Code quickstart docs bundled at /usr/share/vibeos/claude-code-docs/.
  * @anthropic-ai/claude-code npm package baked via mkosi.postinst.chroot.

